text: Punta Lobos is a headland and was a launch site for sounding rockets in Peru at . Between 1980 and 1990, various rockets of the type super Loki, Nike Orion, Taurus Orion and Taurus Tomahawk were launched there. ==External links== *Rocket launch site Punta Lobos Category:Headlands of Peru Category:Rocket launch sites
